{"tid":1853113,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【修正 + 重開】求下你哋唔好再吹戴豬嘴出街","createTime":"2020-01-30T19:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T21:53:36.000Z","uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"02b2ab480d09bc475aa3f572eeba5edf5cb34f8c","tid":1853113,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:12:20.000Z","msg":"頭先開過一個post<br />\n<br />\n求下你哋唔好再吹戴豬嘴出街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1852774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1852774</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n但經過眾多巴絲嘅提點後<br />\n<br />\n我決定重開過個post<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我知我上個post柒咗<br />\n<br />\n屌得細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>其實戴豬嘴出街並冇問題<br />\n<br />\n有問題嘅係你後續清潔<br />\n<br />\n永遠吹戴豬嘴嘅post<br />\n<br />\n都係大篇幅咁樣講濾罐 / 濾棉<br />\n<br />\n而冇乜點樣講過清潔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清潔係一個好大嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n你唔識清潔嘅話<br />\n<br />\n同你戴同一個外科口罩兩日一樣<br />\n<br />\n係非常危險 + 污糟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先<br />\n<br />\n<del>你一定要用濃度高過75%酒精清潔</del><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係用1 : 99 嘅漂白水</span><br />\n<br />\n<del>簡單啲嚟講<br />\n<br />\n你支清潔劑嘅成本<br />\n<br />\n會比起你每日戴N95出街更加高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n<br />\n你一定要disassembly 成個豬嘴去清潔<br />\n<br />\n塑膠嘅部分要每一part每一part咁清潔<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔做<br />\n<br />\n啲罅位 / valve 係極容易滋生細菌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果係布料 ( 頭帶 )<br />\n<br />\n一定要用完即棄<br />\n<br />\n因為你冇辦法徹底清潔佢</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以總括而言<br />\n<br />\n除非你去到一個口罩都冇 ( 無論係外科定n95 )<br />\n<br />\n你先好用豬嘴<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係<br />\n<br />\n會危險過你戴普通外科口罩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀 : <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=d4fe0540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a><br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n下面係上一個post嘅巴絲留下嘅有用comment <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我都覺得有罩唔應該用豬咀，但原來3m係有文件講豬咀用係healthcare，佢入面都講係可以重用filter，每次用完用酒精清潔表面，同埋佢用7093/6035<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4R5cJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4R5cJf.jpg&h=589fd24b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s18OUWB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs18OUWB.jpg&h=6c7c1f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKMwSJh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKMwSJh.jpg&h=af5bd0a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsVqcJi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsVqcJi.jpg&h=a30afec7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yUneWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yUneWE.jpg&h=c49dfd8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n咪講左一定要完全清潔囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無得揀先帶姐<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>好<br />\nsorry巴打我語氣重左<br />\n但首先抹都會有機會令度表面嘅膠溶化，唔會係好似糖溶係水咁溶，而係逐啲逐啲蝕左<br />\n要睇唔同型號用唔同材料造<br />\n7字頭係silicone造好似就無大影響<br />\n但其他有塑膠部件嘅型號用有機溶劑清潔就有可能導致舊膠蝕左<br />\n嚴重可以影響氣密性！！！<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下點樣可以漂白水未必消毒到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>所謂有機物係有carbon做膽嘅就係organic野<br />\n所以其他無carbon嘅例如ammonia雙氧水都可以<br />\n不過ammonia臭到冤<br />\n雙氧水同漂白水係最容易攞到而有效嘅清潔劑</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a69bc663821af4273e0c0382b6e360a69326a11","tid":1853113,"uid":254456,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係隔離豬嘴post回左，我係呢邊都貼一次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK540078/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK540078%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=bcb8db5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK540078/</a><br />\n呢本ebook係美國National Academies of Sciences分析同收集豬嘴(Elastomeric Respirators)用係<span style=\"color: gold;\"></span>醫護身上嘅可行性同效能，如果你地真係諗住用建議研究下先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>TLDR結論:豬嘴+P100係你無哂口罩之下嘅最後手段，佢係防護上係有效，但點先可以安全重用就未有足夠研究support，除罩同消毒做得唔好甚至有可能增加你中招風險</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>效能:</strong></span><br />\n係無做過Fit test嘅情況之下，豬嘴+P100普遍比N95更大機會貼面做到氣密，而過濾效能亦同N95同級或更高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>問題</strong></span><br />\n1.豬嘴filter嘅壽命係視乎佢曝露係咩污染物同有幾高濃度，而對病毒黎講係無任何數據可以話你知Filter幾時要換<br />\n2.除豬嘴果時用咩步驟可以盡量減低污染自己嘅機會同樣無指引，而SARS果時亦有醫護係除保護衣(de-gowning)果時做得唔好而中招<br />\n3.用咩方法消毒個豬嘴係可以消滅到痴係上面嘅病毒?<br />\n3.1呢點亦都係無足夠研究可以比到建議，但可以參考下表3個用H1N1流感病毒嘅實驗結果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK540078/table/tab_2-4/?report=objectonly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK540078%2Ftable%2Ftab_2-4%2F%3Freport%3Dobjectonly&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=daaa4872\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK540078/table/tab_2-4/?report=objectonly</a><br />\n- Cell culture=消完毒再試下個豬嘴上邊嘅H1N1流感病毒仲有無感染細胞嘅能力<br />\n- PCR=睇下消完毒之報仲搵唔到H1N1流感病毒嘅遺存物質(RNA)，不過作者亦都提到入邊嘅消毒方法亦唔係針對破壞病毒嘅RNA，加上啲病毒無左個蛋白質外殼已經無左感染能力，所以check到有都唔代表啲咩<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">3.2作者話豬嘴果兩條頭帶因為材料問題好難用消毒wipe清潔乾淨，所以係最常搵到有病毒嘅零件，大家要留意</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">現實上用醫護用豬嘴嘅例子</span></strong><br />\n2009年美國爆H1N1豬流感，University of Maryland Medical Center係唔夠口罩之下試左用豬嘴+P100 filter<br />\n以下係當時嘅指引:(佢地嘅做法唔一定係最好或最安全，只供參考)<br />\nUsers were provided with instructions for use and with alcohol wipes for facepiece cleaning and were told to store their assigned respirator in a gallon plastic reclosable bag. Protocol required that users wash their assigned respirator weekly<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">關於無cover P100 filter (3M 2097/2091)可唔可以用酒精消毒，可參考K Kwong</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n又有人問，能否在口罩底面噴上一層消毒酒精？K Kwong指，外科口罩之所以能夠抵擋病毒，是因為病毒（體積約0.1微米）和飛沫（體積約5至10微米）混在一起後體積變大，而外科口罩一般可阻隔3微米以上飛沫。 而酒精會蒸發水份，如果在口罩底面噴上酒精，就有機會只蒸發了飛沫中的水份，但又未必足以毀滅病毒；當只剩下體積十分細小的病毒時，外科口罩未能有效阻隔，就有機會令我們直接吸入。<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200130/NZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200130%2FNZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=306b2077\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200130%2FNZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4%2F&h=83feec10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200130/NZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外建議大家睇埋呢位巴打嘅post了解下關於病毒嘅基本智識<br />\n大學讀病毒學，你問，我盡量答 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1844443/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1844443/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面打唔曬<br />\n<br />\n呢個都係另外一位巴打有用嘅comment"},{"pid":"9763055becd82fd5d50bd448f1be8811eacd2cc0","tid":1853113,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:22:42.000Z","msg":"柒就要認<br />\n<br />\n屌就要企定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過屌得細力D<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"bbbb91262593a6a8dd48c74903095796ea39a410","tid":1853113,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文得殘體字<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.3mfangdumianju.cn/article/60.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.3mfangdumianju.cn%2Farticle%2F60.html&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=eab93b14\